import React from 'react' import PropTypes from 'prop-types' import './cta.css' const CTA = (props) => (
{props.heading1}

{props.content1}

{props.action1}
) CTA.defaultProps = { heading1: 'Get Started with MadeforMe', content1: 'Wether you are a maker or buyer, we would love for you to join our community. Fill out the form to get started as soon as the MadeforMe launches.', action1: 'Fill out form', } CTA.propTypes = { heading1: PropTypes.string, content1: PropTypes.string, action1: PropTypes.string, } export default CTA
